Package: RSQLite.toolkit
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight toolkit to load data in SQLite from tabular files
Version: 0.0.0.9905
Authors@R: 
    person("Ludovico G.", "Beretta", , "ludovicogiovanni.beretta@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A lightweight wrapper around the RSQLite package for streamlined loading of
    data from tabular files (i,e. text delimited files like CSV and TSV, Microsoft Excel,
    and Arrow IPC files) in a SQLite databases.
    Includes helper functions for inspecting the structure of the input files, and
    some functions to simplify activities on the SQLite tables.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports:
	DBI,
	RSQLite,
	openxlsx2,
	arrow
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://github.com/fab-algo/RSQLite.toolkit
BugReports: https://github.com/fab-algo/RSQLite.toolkit/issues
